Selain itu,

00:28:51.040 --> 00:28:52.480
sebelum dia jatuh sakit,

00:28:53.400 --> 00:28:54.560
bukankah dia memegangnya

00:28:54.640 --> 00:28:55.780
seperti biji matanya?

